Privacy Policy for WiseWords - Daily Quotes

At WiseWords - Daily Quotes, accessible from [insert app store link], one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by WiseWords - Daily Quotes and how we use it.

If you have additional questions or require more information about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us.

Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information from our users such as name, address, email, phone number, or any other identifying information.

We do collect anonymous usage statistics to help us improve the app. This includes data such as how often the app is used, which features are used most frequently, and any errors that occur while using the app.

Third-Party Services

WiseWords - Daily Quotes uses third-party services to provide certain features and functions within the app. These services may collect and use information in accordance with their own privacy policies.

Firebase Crashlytics: We use Firebase Crashlytics to collect crash reports when the app experiences an error. The data collected is anonymous and is used to help us identify and fix issues with the app.
Google Analytics for Firebase: We use Google Analytics for Firebase to collect anonymous usage statistics. This data is used to help us understand how users interact with the app and to improve its features and functionality.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at foisonpro@gmail.com
